@@WMarble Ring@@N~
The marble facing on the third tier has been supplemented with practical granite reinforcements at ground level, where cart wheels and heavy traffic have chipped the softer stone. The contrast between the white marble above and the dark granite below creates a distinctive banded appearance that local residents use as a landmark when giving directions. A municipal drinking fountain set into the eastern wall provides clean water piped from the temple district cisterns.
