The Auburn Traverse descends slightly as the corridor transitions from the commercial-shop tier into the lower residential and outfitting quarter. The paving stones here are a mix of old red clay brick and newer granite patches, evidence of repeated repair work necessitated by the heavy cart traffic that passes through this section daily. A @@Wposted notice@@N on the wall advertises the services of nearby armourers and clothiers, its ink smudged by rain and handling but still legible to anyone willing to stand close and squint.
