@@yNorthwall Astral Gate@@N~
Bronze astrolabes and rotating mirrors frame the northern breach in @@WMidgaard@@N's defensive perimeter where scholars and dimensional travelers chart impossible constellations before committing to the roads beyond the city walls. The passage bends into geometries that the eye refuses to resolve — the @@castral planes@@N pressing close against the thinned boundary between the material city and the spaces beyond it. City stewards have reinforced this junction with extra @@ylanterns@@N, @@cwarding sigils@@N painted in phosphorescent blue on the archway stones, and civic notices reminding travelers to register their destination with the Ward Office before departure. The gate sees steady traffic from arcanists, planar researchers, and the occasional adventurer drawn by reports of phenomena in the regions accessible through the breach. A carved stone lintel above the gate bears the inscription of the @@pViolet Compact's@@N Article Seven, which requires all extraplanar transit points within the city limits to maintain minimum staffing and illumination at all hours.
